text:
@mkfilko Pain! My main holds AAOI and $SIVE

🫪 I took today to shift some losses into IQE since I think there is a quick rebound

Plus tomorrow US markets are closed so Europe has 1 extra trading day - should be able to let me swing trade some gains into some oversold photonics by Monday

embedded_text:
@ram_blings NP, I'm not sure if people remember this but $SIVE went up +70% in a day off $GFS news. And $AAOI has random +20-30% days. 

They're also capable of doing the opposite. 

Photonics sector are very volatile, but directionally they follow fundamentals in the long run.

